{"tid":1296182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：撐警集會有人違法與集會無關","createTime":"2019-07-08T09:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:08:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":801,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"8784057331cd04f3a168550fa1b9fa2ed2fe8d6c","tid":1296182,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯出席一個網台節目後被問到，有人被指在撐警集會中作出違法行為，他回應稱，完全不認同任何暴力及違法行為，事件亦<span style=\"color: red;\">與集會無關</span>。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，修訂《逃犯條例》本來是為了完善社會、司法系統等，但如果未能得到廣泛市民的支持，亦不應勉強。他認為，今次的修例風波是不必要，是有人<span style=\"color: red;\">誤導群眾</span>，條例本身並非23條，批評有人指通過條例後，香港市民會被移交到內地的說法是<span style=\"color: red;\">誇張失實</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於條例何時會再討論，何君堯表示，要視乎政府的要求，但長遠而言再次提交條例到立法會是完全無問題，因為全世界都有這類條例，中國亦已與55個國家簽訂有關協議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186064/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2186064%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=49227d89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186064/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dde56690d09597e11a9347224fd094fc4cd303f","tid":1296182,"uid":28558,"like":311,"dislike":0,"score":311,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"又割"},{"pid":"21c644d4cd15307ac974d9d7a9d5de8adc404781","tid":1296182,"uid":212626,"like":187,"dislike":0,"score":187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"何君妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d914887c918244ccc7146647527099fe408fc4f7","tid":1296182,"uid":3358,"like":339,"dislike":0,"score":339,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:43:27.000Z","msg":"警察唔帶委任證又同警察有冇關？"},{"pid":"4668fbdda6978d0e7b1c338b526c837ba7be7a46","tid":1296182,"uid":212626,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:44:01.000Z","msg":"仲有一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何君堯：不起訴被捕示威者將人凌駕法律上<br />\n<br />\n大批市民昨日在反修例遊行結束後，轉往佔據旺角彌敦道一帶馬路，警方晚上11時前採取驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯在網台節目上表示，不認為修訂《逃犯條例》是惡法，條例本身已考慮人權，不會將港人無緣無故移交內地。市民以激烈方式表達意見時，亦需要知道界線在哪裏，市民不要人云亦云。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於有人要求不起訴因反修例而被捕示威者，他指出，有關訴求將人凌駕在法律之上。若成立獨立調查委員會，不應只調查警方執法行動，而是要檢視整件事件。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186053/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2186053%2F&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e6652e28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186053/</a>"},{"pid":"f6b0073e57b2b38c0da8e4ea7685ce15ebc78112","tid":1296182,"uid":130695,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"55個窮閪食人生畜國<br />\n支那去返人食人啦"},{"pid":"85f52ce8956d26d9ed6354c29f777bf2c410297b","tid":1296182,"uid":191740,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"割割割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31ec68f069552d19189f06f55de67f5824fd2ea","tid":1296182,"uid":23162,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"呢條真仆街嚟，無論藍黃都應該屌爆何君妖呢條大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a93b9c964dc520f1358817324cccc7810aa9e4","tid":1296182,"uid":166506,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番去執樹葉啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf33a50dc8a6a345949365bae275f5864350101f","tid":1296182,"uid":21