整件事件。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Deal</span></span>"},{"pid":"50ce6fbb30e97f6af22f675a251d83fe647eacfd","tid":1296182,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"邊個割先 邊個輸先都未明"},{"pid":"098687aa18c6f2df1161c12129b3000b63303131","tid":1296182,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:48:34.000Z","msg":"對於有人要求不起訴因反修例而被捕示威者，他指出，有關訴求將人凌駕在法律之上。<span style=\"color: red;\">若成立獨立調查委員會，不應只調查警方執法行動，而是要檢視整件事件。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d18a03a623bacaf660f76a298b7fbeea513df55","tid":1296182,"uid":12412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:48:34.000Z","msg":"彩就你攞屎就人哋食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5a06b8b9478bd6a71149dac928addb47b8f2b3","tid":1296182,"uid":98425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1efc8cec287f4847f78a6fa696f45b4e4069213f","tid":1296182,"uid":4597,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"藍絲比人當棄子，譚校脹快啲出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"藍絲都condom化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516d7eeb1f1614affbe20d2bc1abee29af478803","tid":1296182,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"學人割蓆先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為主辦單位，無控制場面！可惡！<br />\n應該取消往後的申請，以儆效尤！"},{"pid":"596f95b478176ce41cb0fb5a0e8be582a0b28588","tid":1296182,"uid":222092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"何君妖講嘢同香港無關。<br />\n可唔可以唔報道。"},{"pid":"b0bde73ffaede8167b6bb3f75d53eb5af6497c28","tid":1296182,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor